Tree and stem tables from Barro Colorado Island (bci).

Source: R/data-census.R

For a general description see census_description. These datasets are tree and stem tables of the same trees selected to create the tables bci_vft_1ha and bci_vft_random. In the name of the tree and stem tables documented here, the number after stem or census matches a value of the column PlotCensusNumber in the corresponding ViewFullTable.

bci_stem6_1ha

bci_stem7_1ha

bci_tree6_1ha

bci_tree7_1ha

bci_stem6_random

bci_stem7_random

bci_tree6_random

bci_tree7_random

Format

See examples.

See also

bci_vft_1ha, bci_vft_random, census_description.
